By: Susan Wirth-White |  Jul 21, 2017



We applied for the Chase Sapphire Preferred card last year and it has become the best credit card that I have ever owned. Customer service is first class and you speak to a person when you call. I redeemed miles for a trip recently and though I could not get the exact departure date, the day earlier worked fine. When I try to book with another card on American, I can never get the dates that I want or I have to use extra miles. It became so frustrating and now I can say, I have found THE CARD that works for us.


